<p>of aeroplanes flying about and any amount of aerial duels, but up to present both sides have failed to bring any down. We expect to do 4 days out here and then 4 days in front line. Enemy plane brought down in flames this afternoon 17.8.16</p>
<p>We took over part of firing line today and had about 40 casualties. Our H.Q. is in another German dugout. Over the top of this dugout is a beautiful bell taken from the Church Spire of Pozieres</p>
